column5: I'm thinking of giving Scugog a go tomorrow for ducks, but I'm a little unsure of the grey area regarding Sunday hunting. I look at the map and it looks like the north end is ok for Sunday.  Can a fella get a hand?
I'd think you would be ok if you are on the City of Kawartha Lakes side of the lake.
Can't help you out bud. Just wanted to bump it forward for ya.  Cheers, Ron...
Yep, the city of kawartha lakes allows sunday gun hunting, just make sure that's where you are set up.  S.
